Interface IndexedValueConverter<OBJ>

  • Type Parameters:
    OBJ - type of object containing the data
    All Superinterfaces:
    ValueConverter<OBJ>
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    CollectionEntryValueConverter

    public interface IndexedValueConverter<OBJ>
extends ValueConverter<OBJ>
    This subinterface of ValueConverter provides access to indexed data from a source.

    Jesse Gallagher
